Basic Terminal Commands

ctrl+shift+	-->	size up
ctrl-		-->	size down
ctrl+A  	--> 	start line
ctrl+E  	--> 	end line
ctrl+w		-->	one word delete
ctrl+U		-->	full line delete
ctrl+C          -->     interupt
su              -->     switch user root to current directory
su -            -->     switch user root to /root directory

Keys in keyboard

~       -->     tilda
`       -->     backtick
!       -->     bang (exclamation)
#       -->     hashtag (pound)
$       -->     dollar (scripting) (invariable)
%       -->     percentage
^       -->     carrot
*       -->     aesterisk (star)
|       -->     pipe
/       -->     forward slash
\       -->     backward slash

